      "created_at": "2024-10-03T13:16:14.487Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi everyone,</p>\n<p>yesterday i did a workout that was supposed to be at 40 rpm in zone 3 wattage.<br>\nI used Erg mode but it seemeed too hard when lowering my cadence.<br>\nat one point i went too low with cadence, about 25, and the resistance went so hard that i had to shift to \u201cresistance mode\u201d.<br>\nAlso, using resistance mode with same cadence and more wattage seemed easier than erg.<br>\nI\u2019m using an Elite suito as trainer, is there something i\u2019m missing?</p>",
