      "created_at": "2024-10-09T14:19:33.551Z",
      "cooked": "<p>That\u2019s called ERG spiral of death or lockdown. As you lower your cadence, the trainer continually adds resistance, until the force becomes so large that you cannot overcome it. 40 rpm is very low for ERG and as you say it\u2019s easy to go too low and get locked out. It\u2019s expected behaviour. If you want to do that kind of training, resistance mode is your friend indeed.</p>",
